      • findByAvailableInDate

        @Query(value="select s from Staff s  where s.staffType.staffType in (\'FITTEST CST\', \'OSTF Dubai\', \'OSTF Rome\') and  not (s in (select distinct(s2) from Staff s2 join s2.staffRoles sr where sr.startDate <= :date and sr.endDate >= :date))")
List<Staff> findByAvailableInDate(@Param(value="date")
                                      Date date)
        Returns a list of Staff who are not assigned to any ActivityRole during the date specified.

        The only StaffTypes considered are FITTEST CST, OSTF Dubai, and OSTF Rome.

        Parameters:
        date -
        Returns:
        A list of available Staff

      • findByNotAvailableInDate

        @Query(value="select distinct(s) from Staff s join s.staffRoles sr where s.staffType.staffType in (\'FITTEST CST\', \'OSTF Dubai\', \'OSTF Rome\') and  sr.startDate <= :date and sr.endDate >= :date")
List<Staff> findByNotAvailableInDate(@Param(value="date")
                                         Date date)
        Returns a list of Staff who are assigned to an ActivityRole during the date specified.

        The only StaffTypes considered are FITTEST CST, OSTF Dubai, and OSTF Rome.

        Parameters:
        date -
        Returns:
        A list of Staff assigned to an ActivityRole during the date given.
